Thank you for visiting! Please feel free to leave a note, I‚Äôd love to hear from you.



                  A foreword... 



I prefer organic entries over automated ones ‚Äî no bots allowed. Feel free to leave feedback on my projects, suggest a book for my reading list, or just say bonjour. If you encounter a bug or an accessibility barrier (especially regarding screen readers or Braille compatibility), you can let me know here or, alternatively, email me.





                  Oh, and... 



To keep this form from abuse, I manually approve entries. Please be aware that if your message is helpful, kind, or interesting, it may be archived here permanently.


